I chose these apps because I learned from them a lot and they all were challenging.
Each of these apps has its own purpose and are used worldwide.
I believe that what I learned most from these apps are new architectures, programming skills and approaches, think quicker, how to give my best in team-work and, best of all, always search for best solutions in licenced resources


